\c 10
\s Umbono kaKorneliyu
\p
\v 1 Kwakukhona eKesariya indoda ethile ngebizo nguKorneliyu\x + 10.24. 8.40.\x*, induna yekhulu yebutho elithiwa ngeleIthaliya\x + Joha. 18.3.\x*,
\v 2 eqotho\x + 10.7. 22.12. 2 Pet. 2.9.\x* lemesabayo uNkulunkulu kanye lendlu yayo yonke, eyenza imisebenzi yomusa eminengi ebantwini, ikhuleka njalonjalo kuNkulunkulu\x + 10.22,35. 13.16,26.\x*;
\v 3 yabona\x + 10.30. 11.13. Hlu. 6.12.\x* embonweni ngokucacileyo, ngokungaba lihola \w lesificamunwemunye\w** losuku\x + 10.17. 12.9.\x*, ingilosi kaNkulunkulu ingena kuyo\x + 12.7.\x*, yasisithi kuyo: Korneliyu!
\v 4 Waseyijolozela\x + Luka 4.20.\x* efikelwa yikwesaba wathi: Kuyini, Nkosi\x + Luka 1.12.\x*? Yasisithi kuye: Imikhuleko yakho lezipho zakho kubayanga kwenyuke\x + Isam. 8.4. Dan. 10.12.\x* kwaba yisikhumbuzo phambi kukaNkulunkulu\x + Mat. 26.13. Mark. 14.9. Seb. 10.31. Heb. 6.10.\x*.
\v 5 Khathesi-ke thuma amadoda eJopha\x + 9.36,43.\x*, ubize uSimoni othiwa futhi nguPetro;
\v 6 yena ungenisile kuSimoni othile umtshuki wezikhumba, ondlu yakhe iselwandle\x + 9.43.\x*; yena uzakutshela ofanele ukwenze\x + 10.22. 11.14.\x*.
\v 7 Kwathi ingilosi ebikhuluma loKorneliyu isihambile, wabiza ababili kwabendlu yakhe\x + Luka 16.13. Roma 14.4. 1 Pet. 2.18.\x*, lowebutho oqotho\x + 10.7. 22.12. 2 Pet. 2.9.\x* kulabo ababemlinda\x + 8.13.\x*,
\v 8 njalo eselandisile konke kubo, wabathuma eJopha.
\s Ukuhlehliswa kwengqondo kaPetro
\p
\v 9 Njalo kusisa bona besahamba sebesondela emzini, uPetro wenyukela\x + 11.5-14.\x* phezu kophahla lwendlu ukuyakhuleka\x + 2 Sam. 11.2.\x*, okungaba lihola \w lesithupha\w**\x + Hlab. 55.17.\x*;
\v 10 waselamba kakhulu, wafuna ukudla; kwathi bona besamlungisela, ukuhlehliswa kwengqondo kwamehlela\x + 22.17.\x*,
\v 11 wasebona izulu livulekile\x + 7.56. Hez. 1.1.\x*, lesitsha esithile sehlela kuye, njengelembu elikhulu, libotshwe ngamasondo amane, lisehliselwa emhlabeni;
\v 12 okwakukhona kulo \add izidalwa\add* zonke ezilenyawo ezine zomhlaba lezeganga lezihuquzelayo lenyoni zezulu.
\v 13 Kwasekufika ilizwi kuye \add lathi\add*: Sukuma, Petro, hlaba udle.
\v 14 Kodwa uPetro wathi: Hatshi bo, Nkosi; ngoba kangizake ngidle loba yini\x + Hez. 4.14. Dan. 1.8.\x* engahlambulukanga\x + 10.28. 11.8. Mark. 7. 2.\x* kumbe engcolileyo\x + Levi 11.2-47. 20.25. Dute. 14.4-20.\x*.
\v 15 Ilizwi laphinda ngokwesibili kuye: Izinto uNkulunkulu azihlambululileyo, wena ungatsho ukuthi kazihlambulukanga\x + Mat. 15.11,18,20. Mark. 7.15,18,20,23. Roma 14.17,20. 1 Kor. 10.25. 1 Tim. 4.4. Tit. 1.15.\x*.
\v 16 Njalo lokhu kwenzeka kwaze kwaba kathathu; lesitsha sabuya saphakanyiselwa ezulwini.
\v 17 Kwathi uPetro esadidekile ngaphakathi kwakhe\x + Luka 9.7.\x* ukuthi ngabe uyini umbono awubonileyo\x + 10.17. 12.9.\x*, njalo khangela, amadoda ayethunywe evela kuKorneliyu, esebuzile indlu kaSimoni, ema\x + 11.11.\x* esangweni\x + Luka 16.20.\x*,
\v 18 esememezile abuza ukuthi uSimoni, othiwa futhi nguPetro, ungenisile lapha yini.
\v 19 Kwathi uPetro esanakana ngombono, uMoya wathi kuye: Khangela, amadoda amathathu ayakudinga\x + 10.7.\x*.
\v 20 Ngakho sukuma wehle, uhambe lawo\x + 15.7-9. Efe. 3.6. Joha. 16.13.\x*, ungathandabuzi\x + Mat. 21.21.\x*; ngoba yimi engiwathumileyo.
\v 21 UPetro wasesehlela emadodeni avela kuKorneliyu ayethunywe kuye, wathi: Khangelani, yimi elimdingayo; yisizatho bani elize ngaso?
\v 22 Basebesithi: UKorneliyu induna yekhulu, indoda elungileyo lemesabayo uNkulunkulu\x + 10.2.\x*, efakazelwa yisizwe sonke samaJuda\x + 6.3.\x*, walayelwa nguNkulunkulu\x + Luka 2.26.\x* ngengilosi engcwele ukuthi akubizele endlini yakhe\x + Mat. 25.31.\x*, njalo ezwe amazwi kuwe\x + 10.6. 11.14.\x*.
\v 23 Ngakho esebabizele phakathi wa\add ba\add*ngenisa. Njalo kusisa uPetro waphuma wahamba labo, labanye\x + 10.45. 11.12.\x* babazalwane ababeseJopha bahamba laye\x + Joha. 21.23.\x*.
\s Ukufika kukaPetro endlini kaKorneliyu
\p
\v 24 Ngosuku olulandelayo basebengena eKesariya\x + 10.1.\x*. LoKorneliyu wayebalindele, esebizele ndawonye izihlobo zakhe labangane abazwana laye.
\v 25 Kwathi sekwenzakele ukuthi uPetro angene, uKorneliyu wamhlangabeza, ewela enyaweni \add zakhe\x + 16.29.\x*\add*, wa\add m\add*khonza\x + Mat. 8.2.\x*.
\v 26 Kodwa uPetro emphakamisa, wathi: Sukuma; lami ngokwami ngingumuntu\x + Isam. 19.10. 22.9. Seb. 14.15. Dan. 2.46.\x*.
\v 27 Njalo esakhuluma layo wangena, wafica abanengi bebuthene\x + 10.24.\x*,
\v 28 wasesithi kubo: Lina liyazi ukuthi kakuvunyelwa emuntwini ongumJuda\x + 1 Pet. 4.3.\x* ukuhlangana kumbe ukuya emuntwini wesinye isizwe\x + Joha. 4.9. 18.28. Seb. 11.3. Gal. 2.12,14.\x*; kodwa uNkulunkulu ungitshengisile ukuthi ngingabizi muntu ngokuthi kahlambulukanga kumbe ungcolile\x + 10.15.\x*;
\v 29 ngakho-ke ngizile ngingaphikisanga nxa ngibizwa. Ngakho ngiyabuza, ukuthi ungibizele sizatho bani?
\v 30 UKorneliyu wasesithi: Ngensuku ezine ezidlulileyo\x + 10.9,23,24.\x* kuze kube yilelihola ngangizila ukudla\x + Mat. 17.21.\x*, ngehola lesificamunwemunye ngangikhuleka endlini yami\x + 3.1.\x*; njalo khangela, indoda yema phambi kwami\x + 1.10.\x* yembethe isembatho esikhazimulayo\x + Luka 23.11.\x*\x + 1.10.\x*,
\v 31 yasisithi: Korneliyu, umkhuleko wakho uzwakele, lemisebenzi yakho yomusa ikhunjulwe phambi kukaNkulunkulu\x + 10.4.\x*.
\v 32 Ngakho thumela eJopha, ubusubiza uSimoni othiwa futhi nguPetro; yena ungenisile endlini kaSimoni umtshuki wezikhumba ngaselwandle; ozakuthi angabuya akutshele\x + 10.5,6.\x*.
\v 33 Ngakho ngahle ngathumela kuwe; njalo wena wenze kuhle ukuthi ufike. Ngakho khathesi sesikhona sonke phambi kukaNkulunkulu ukuze sizwe konke okulayelwe nguNkulunkulu\x + 2 Pet. 1.19. 3 Joha. 6.\x*.
\s Intshumayelo kaPetro
\p
\v 34 Kwathi uPetro evula umlomo, wathi\x + Mat. 5.2.\x*: Ngeqiniso ngiyaqedisisa ukuthi uNkulunkulu kayisuye umkhangeli wobuso bomuntu\x + Dute. 10.17.\x*;
\v 35 kodwa kuso sonke isizwe\x + 15.9. Roma 2.13,26,27. 3.22,29. 10.12,13. 1 Kor. 12.13. Gal. 3.28. Efe. 2.13,18. 3.6.\x* yena omesabayo lowenza ukulunga, uyemukeleka kuye\x + 10.2.\x*.
\v 36 Ilizwi alithumela kubantwana bakoIsrayeli, ngevangeli etshumayela ukuthula ngoJesu Kristu\x + Luka 2.14.\x* (yena\x + Mat. 28.18. Roma 10.12. Isam. 17.14.19.16.\x* uyiNkosi yabo bonke\x + 2.36. Luka 2.11.\x*).
\v 37 Lina liyalazi ilizwi elamenyezelwa eJudiya yonke, kusukela eGalili\x + Mat. 4.12. Mark. 1.14. Luka 4.14. Joha. 4.43.\x*, emva kobhabhathizo uJohane alutshumayelayo;
\v 38 uJesu weNazaretha, ukuthi uNkulunkulu wamgcoba njani ngoMoya oNgcwele langamandla\x + 4.27. 2.22.\x*, owabhoda esenza okulungileyo njalo esilisa bonke labo abacindezelwe ngudiyabhola, ngoba uNkulunkulu wayelaye\x + Joha. 3.2.\x*.
\v 39 Lathi singabafakazi bezinto zonke azenzayo elizweni lamaJuda leJerusalema\x + 10.41. 2.32.\x*; abambulala ba\add m\add*phanyeka esihlahleni\x + 5.30. 2.23.\x*.
\v 40 Yena uNkulunkulu wamvusa ngosuku lwesithathu, wasemnika ukuze abonakale\x + 2.24.\x*,
\v 41 kungeyisikho kubo bonke abantu\x + Joha. 14.17,22.\x*, kodwa kubafakazi ababekhethwe ngaphambili nguNkulunkulu\x + 10.39.13.31. Luka 24.48.\x*, kithi, esadla sanatha kanye laye emva kokuvuka kwakhe kwabafileyo\x + Luka 24.30,43. Joha. 21.12,13. Seb. 1.4.\x*.
\v 42 Wasesilaya ukuthi sitshumayele ebantwini\x + Mat. 28.19,20. Seb. 1.2.\x*, sifakaze\x + Luka 16.28.\x* ukuthi nguye\x + Joha. 5.22,27. Seb. 17.31.\x* omiswe nguNkulunkulu ukuba nguMehluli\x + Luka 22.22.\x* wabaphilayo labafileyo\x + Roma 14.9. 2 Tim. 4.1. 1 Pet. 4.5. 1 Thes. 4.15-17. Roma 14.10.\x*.
\v 43 Ngaye bonke abaprofethi bafakaza\x + Jer. 31.34. Mika 7.18. Seb. 26.22.\x*, ukuthi wonke okholwa kuye\x + 13.39.15.9. Roma 10.11. Gal. 3.22.\x* uzakwemukela uthethelelo lwezono ngebizo lakhe\x + 5.31.\x*.
\s Ukubhabhathizwa kukaKorneliyu labendlu yakhe
\p
\v 44 Kwathi uPetro esakhuluma lawomazwi, uMoya oyiNgcwele wehlela phezu kwabo bonke abalizwayo ilizwi\x + 11.15. 2.4.\x*.
\v 45 Labokusoka abakholwayo basanganiseka\x + 10.23. 11.12.\x*, bonke ababefike loPetro\x + 10.23. 11.12.\x*, ukuthi isipho sikaMoya oNgcwele\x + 2.38.\x* sathululelwa\x + 2.33.\x* laphezu kwabezizwe\x + 11.18. Mat. 8.11.\x*;
\v 46 ngoba babezwa bekhuluma ngendimi, bekhulisa uNkulunkulu\x + 19.6. 2.4.\x*. Khona uPetro waphendula \add wathi\x + 3.12.5.8. Hlu. 18.14.\x*\add*:
\v 47 Ukhona yini ongala lamanzi, ukuthi laba bangabhabhathizwa\x + 8.36. 11.17.\x*, abemukele uMoya oyiNgcwele lanjengathi\x + 11.17. 15.8,9. Roma 10.12.\x*?
\v 48 Waselaya ukuthi babhabhathizwe\x + 1 Kor. 1.14-17.\x* ebizweni leNkosi\x + 2.38. 8.16. 19.5. Mat. 28.19.\x*. Basebemcela ukuthi ahlale insuku ezithile.
